# Phase 3 â€” File Server & Shared Folders

# Overview
Created department-based shared folders with strict Linux permissions and Samba for file sharing.

# 1. Shared Folder Structure with Permissions
sudo mkdir -p /company/shared/{hr,engineering,sales,general}
sudo chmod 770 /company/shared/hr
sudo chmod +t /company/shared/hr
ls -la /company/shared/

![Shared Folders](https://github.com/NikJGFrancis/company-it-lab/blob/main/Company%20IT%20Lab%20Screenshots/Shared%20Folders.png)

# 2. Access Control Test

Verified that users can only access their own department folders.
su - alice
ls /company/shared/engineering   # Permission denied

![Access Control Test](https://github.com/NikJGFrancis/company-it-lab/blob/main/Company%20IT%20Lab%20Screenshots/Alice%20Access%20Controls.png)

# 3. Samba Installed and Running
sudo apt install samba -y
sudo systemctl status smbd

![Samba Running](https://github.com/NikJGFrancis/company-it-lab/blob/main/Company%20IT%20Lab%20Screenshots/systemctl%20status%20smbd%20showing%20active.png)
